  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the microscopic world inside the human body with Bioguard, an amusing and infectious tower defense game with roguelite elements! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use three special resources and upgrades to develop unique strategies for each stage of this biological combat, handling different enemy combinations and level design.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669910/extras/a0abae5ff12bb09ffde934055b243b57.avif?t=1750471309\" width=419 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock unique skills with tower thematics. Use them in key moments during combat to aid your towers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669910/extras/2a93ef9d14cdea0fbd8150c3e6af8a52.poster.avif?t=1750471309\" width=800 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669910/extras/2a93ef9d14cdea0fbd8150c3e6af8a52.webm?t=1750471309\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669910/extras/2a93ef9d14cdea0fbd8150c3e6af8a52.mp4?t=1750471309\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669910/extras/b37ecf62287d622c4a199a1490e36807.avif?t=1750471309\" width=419 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tower are your base defense, use each one of the four towers and its upgrades wisely to take advantage of its specific qualities. Use the ATP gathered by defeating enemies to build these immune defence structures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669910/extras/ccc984aff6ed5b9a97fa827d0a806eb0.poster.avif?t=1750471309\" width=800 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669910/extras/ccc984aff6ed5b9a97fa827d0a806eb0.webm?t=1750471309\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669910/extras/ccc984aff6ed5b9a97fa827d0a806eb0.mp4?t=1750471309\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669910/extras/7bb3abda1fe622da2390faed63cf4028.avif?t=1750471309\" width=419 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put together a deck of cards of diverse effects and buy a card each and every wave. Keep up to three cards in hand and use them to influence game a tower mechanics. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669910/extras/f60bb91d706d1c1f21b349c495cb08cf.avif?t=1750471309\" width=419 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spend the DNA attained by completing levels on new towers, cards, skills and all of its upgrades. Discover the ideal build to beat every new challenge!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the microscopic world inside the human body with Bioguard, an amusing and infectious tower defense game with roguelite elements! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use three special resources and upgrades to develop unique strategies for each stage of this biological combat, handling different enemy combinations and level design.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669910/extras/a0abae5ff12bb09ffde934055b243b57.avif?t=1750471309\" width=419 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock unique skills with tower thematics. Use them in key moments during combat to aid your towers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669910/extras/2a93ef9d14cdea0fbd8150c3e6af8a52.poster.avif?t=1750471309\" width=800 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669910/extras/2a93ef9d14cdea0fbd8150c3e6af8a52.webm?t=1750471309\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669910/extras/2a93ef9d14cdea0fbd8150c3e6af8a52.mp4?t=1750471309\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2669910/extras/b37ecf62287d622c4a199a1490e36807.avif?t=1750471309\" width=419 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tower are your base defense, use each one of the four towers and its upgrades wisely to take advantage of its specific qualities. Use the ATP gathered by defeating enemies to build these immune defence structures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"